# Navigation

## Bottom Toolbar

The toolbar respects the safe area inset on devices with a home indicator.
The toolbar follows iOS Human Interface Guidelines for tab bars.
Icons use SF Symbols:

- Tasks: `checklist`
- Lists: `tray.full`
- Settings: `gearshape`

@ref(https://developer.apple.com/design/human-interface-guidelines/tab-bars)

## Screen Transitions

The swipe-back gesture uses the standard iOS interactive pop transition.
